name: Experiment Or Die #67
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. A scream echoes throughout whether you like it or not. Once it leaves your lungs you can't put it back in. So take care in what you put out into the world. Even if you're underwater think about each breath, compose yourself and claw your way back to the surface! Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
